            "title": "《異動股》聯合能源集團(00467)跌逾一成,現報0.65元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社20日專訊》聯合能源集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00467:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00467\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00467-HK</a>)現跌近11%,最低價見0.65元,最高價0.74元;成交6.88億股,成交金額4.79億元;主動買沽比率37:63,資金淨主動賣出1.19億元。現時最大淨被動買入券商為中國投資信息,金額4006萬元,加權平均成交價0.697元;現時最大淨被動賣出券商為富昌證券,金額790.55萬元,加權平均成交價0.693元。以現價計,該股暫連跌2日,累計跌幅15.6%。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　基本資料</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　====</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>現價</td><td>0.650</td><td>變動</td><td>-10.96%</td></tr><tr><td>最高價</td><td>0.740</td><td>最低價</td><td>0.650</td></tr><tr><td>成交股數</td><td>6.88億股</td><td>成交金額</td><td>4.79億</td></tr><tr><td>10天平均</td><td>0.558</td><td>歷史波幅%</td><td>133.395</td></tr><tr><td>20天平均</td><td>0.482</td><td>加權平均價</td><td>0.696</td></tr><tr><td>50天平均</td><td>0.411</td><td>RSI14</td><td>68.296</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">股份狀態:主動買沽比率37:63,資金淨主動賣出1.19億元;暫連跌2日,累計跌幅15.6%</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>聯合能源集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00467:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00467\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00467-HK</a>)</td><td>0.650</td><td>-10.96</td></tr><tr><td>元亨燃氣(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00332:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00332\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00332-HK</a>)</td><td>0.039</td><td>無升跌</td></tr><tr><td>中石化(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00386:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00386\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00386-HK</a>)</td><td>4.050</td><td>+0.25</td></tr><tr><td>中港石油(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00632:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00632\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00632-HK</a>)</td><td>0.690</td><td>-2.82</td></tr><tr><td>中石油(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00857:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00857\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00857-HK</a>)</td><td>6.740</td><td>-0.88</td></tr><tr><td>中海油(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00883:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00883\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00883-HK</a>)</td><td>17.920</td><td>-0.55</td></tr><tr><td>中信資源(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01205:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01205\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01205-HK</a>)</td><td>0.430</td><td>+4.88</td></tr><tr><td>MI能源(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01555:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01555\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01555-HK</a>)</td><td>0.054</td><td>+3.85</td></tr><tr><td>陽光油砂(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02012:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02012\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02012-HK</a>)</td><td>0.710</td><td>-7.79</td></tr><tr><td>吉星新能源(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03395:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03395\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03395-HK</a>)</td><td>0.800</td><td>-23.81</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(ed)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
